 &lt;h1 id=&#34;register-allocation&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#register-allocation&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Register Allocation&lt;/h1&gt;
